# Claude Code local config (generated, not part of plugin)
# After the multi-target migration, the compiled skill tree lives at ./skills/
# (committed at the repo root, no whitelist needed). Per-target plugin manifests
# live at .claude-plugin/ and .codex-plugin/ at the repo root, also unaffected
# by this rule. .claude/ now only carries local-developer artefacts (settings,
# worktrees) which stay ignored.
/.claude/*
!/.claude/settings.json
